However, Han was also impeached on December 27, 2024, and First Deputy Prime Minister Choi Sang-mok became acting president. Han was later acquitted on March 24, 2025, and returned to his role as acting president, before resigning on May 1, 2025 [wikipedia](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE4qpu76_mqM0bHuTviUbRdvvxS8DKCoIqSHlZxE7q59BNhO5dPfaWebI4VvvVxU5DMDHEi3fcgaU3FbCbSIqMgVlxWFc5s0Bx_qIQ4QKo7POaaVN0mNKCm2qayJk-MSgudWt-8vvQD_gaWCm4i4pMS32ALeoE=) [loc](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHQxla0aCaJnslFOAeFux9_3nM4U8i44si6-VWcU03drUNXtzdpJU8ku4WHW9dhZTCpI_KSkj-lhz6EWiZ9Z184WJNCXTcYMk9X-FU1TCW2ULMEqxGKLBvVwzAqKiBW0QBoCWnWV2yk_5qdACio0mlI1DDUiSfoSaz7rRE8PVFm-bPR_jXbK4QWEAyGu3CGX_aBmP8h3QgVFIHA3lOQwXSD2fsryUAhyCPJBf3d7MHCnwBa3nE4pyWbCLwQdg==)].
